# Contributing to Codex Continuum
1) `make codex-all` locally before opening a PR.  
2) Commit style: Conventional Commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, chore:, refactor:, perf:, test:).  
3) PRs must pass **codex-pr-gate** (policy, tests, seals).  
4) Attestations are append-only. Never rewrite chain history.

